Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.76,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:57.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气弹一出手　炸裂吧飞散吧　Go Go Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:04.61,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘势力　正在某处蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:10.08,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不饶恕　全都给我等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:16.54,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命　我也一定守护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:22.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的勇气　要凭着它来令自己更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:28.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以坚持到底的气势　去跨越每一场危难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:35.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遇强越强的气魄　更兴奋的我迎难而上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:43.19,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着幸运的风  咻咻地飞越穹苍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:55.07,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　明天依然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:02:02.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的灵魂　早已经知晓了所有的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.71,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨轻易地弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔使尽浑身解数的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在绝望气氛弥漫的那个时刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量不断涌出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭，小林，短笛，我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能设法救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟悟空能否拯救同伴呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:38.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:43.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着那无尽的天际飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:46.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高空中驾驭着喷射气流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:48.82,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里　只要想去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.69,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水汽扑面而来　无比惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go tip-top!　All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:22:00.41,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝地球仿佛苏醒　睁开了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:07.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗无可替代的星球　绝不能拱手放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:11.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧炸飞吧　龟派气功波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:14.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个充满危机的时代里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:20.39,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着就要守护这世界　这是我的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:26.56,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手一搏用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.56,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为希望就是我拥有的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:35.24,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对未来我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「打倒弗利萨吧孙悟空！高傲战士贝吉塔之泪」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短笛叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能设法救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊，好像完全丧失斗志了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有点为时过早，不过还是了结你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，果然那股强大的气就是短笛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老孙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，是用龙珠把你送来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，托你们的福伤都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错啊，悟饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说交给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙，打算独自和那个怪物较量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你真的是悟空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的气感觉完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老孙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是老孙吗？强得难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在地球上的他完全不能相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙就是弗利萨啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象中要小得多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，居然还有漏掉的垃圾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和贝吉塔约定好要一决胜负的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙好像在哪见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡卡罗特，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡罗特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个名字听起来是赛亚人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨！给我滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗…弗利萨大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弗利萨大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来，一切都会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙，的确是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗贝吉塔行星的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡罗特的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你这家伙的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一击了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我在毁灭贝吉塔行星的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗到最后一刻的赛亚人长得一摸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡…卡卡罗特…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡罗特啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛亚人一个都不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢，乖乖地躲起来发抖不就没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是从前的那个卡卡罗特了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于克服屏障超越极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好受死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空那家伙做什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都没办法看清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的速度已经超越弗利萨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开，悟空！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，躲开，悟空！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…全部弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只用了单手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨，你还是拿出真本事来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙正是你最为害怕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个传说中的全宇宙最强战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨你已经完蛋了！活该见鬼去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝…贝吉塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道的吧？贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌无聊的笑话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！贝吉塔都已经完全不能动弹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要再对他下毒手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直把超级赛亚人这个无聊的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在嘴边，喋喋不休
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌啰嗦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡卡罗特…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么还在讲那么天真的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是超级赛亚人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！你要变得冷酷无情！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不再天真的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能够变成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法变得像你那样冷酷无情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说，我也不知道所谓的超级赛亚人是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所…所谓的超级赛亚人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只会加速你的死亡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太漂亮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨博先生，多多利亚先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这烟火实在是太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给…给我听好了！卡卡罗特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心脏都被打穿了，还真是顽强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能继续讲话啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和你出生的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔行星消失的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并…并不是因为巨大陨石的撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是弗利萨干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赛亚人对他惟命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全听从他的命令行事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除了我们以外所有人都被他杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你的双亲和我的父亲贝吉塔王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为弗利萨他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕愈战愈勇的赛亚人当中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生出超级赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，你还真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝…贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…把弗利萨…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把弗利萨打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托了！用赛亚人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于咽气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，让我们重新开始恐怖的表演秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定非常不甘心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星上怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝…贝吉塔…是那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，非常轻易地就被弗利萨杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对弗利萨惟命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全听从命令行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却惨遭背叛反被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛亚人的尊严呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗…弗利萨是那么可怕的家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他触及了不该触及的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触犯了不该触犯的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶！这样的家伙做对手就算是悟空也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么悟空他怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗志满满，似乎无论如何也要打倒弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是因为同伴被杀死而不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是一直受那家伙摆布却无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才觉得不甘心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然非常讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一直对自己身为赛亚人引以为傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也分享一下你的那份自豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在地球上长大的赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了被你杀死的赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有，也为了这里的那美克星人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…又开始说废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空身为赛亚人的自豪感也在此刻觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那激怒的力量究竟能否取得胜利呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
